{"search_data": "Central Deen Dayal SPARSH Yojana Scholarship Scheme to Promote Philately \u0939\u093f\u0902\u0926\u0940 \u092e\u0947\u0902 \u092a\u0922\u093c\u0947\u0902Deen Dayal SPARSH Yojana Selection ProcessThe execution department of the scheme will publish the notification to circle-wise enroll students under the scheme.The department will provide the list of topics for projects while issuing the notification of the scheme.Subsequently, the authority will conduct a circle \u2013 wise quiz contest of philately & performance. The performance of quiz will evaluate the eligibility of the student.The department will form a committee at circle level which will consist of postal officials and renowned philatelists. This committee will evaluate the project work on philately submitted by the students.Detailed benefits of Sparsh Yojana can be found on the below link:Deen Dayal Sparsh Yojana BenefitsEligibility Criteria for Deen Dayal SPARSH YojanaInterested student can read the eligibility criteria to avail the scheme below:-The student should be studying in recognized school within India.The student will be selected only from the school which have a Philately Club and the student should have to be a member of that Club.However, if school does not have a Philately Club then a student having his personal Philately deposit account will also be considered.The student should have secured minimum 60% marks in the final year examination and in addition, 5% relaxation will be given to the student belonging to SC /ST community.Moreover, the every prospective school which is participating in the competition would be assigned a Philately mentor to be chosen from the renowned Philatelists. These selected philately mentors will help in the formation of the School level Philately Club.In addition, they would also be providing guidance to young and aspiring Philatelists. They will also guide on how to pursue the hobby and helping the aspiring Philatelists on their Philately Projects etc.The interested candidates can download guidelines of the scheme by clicking on below link.Download Sparsh GuidelinesThe information in the guidelines PDF document is available in both English and Hindi language.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}